use the same components and
felt that those teams

35
00:01:59.856 --> 00:02:04.046
would be able to do everything they
needed with little or no extension.

36
00:02:04.046 --> 00:02:07.314
What it turns out though
that the startup mindset,

37
00:02:07.314 --> 00:02:11.798
that creative culture of the organization
meant they were constantly

38
