your subscribers want to do.

147
00:08:44.036 --> 00:08:47.543
You do that with culture,
not with pixels, not with code or

148
00:08:47.543 --> 00:08:50.571
documentation, not with figma,
not with react.

149
00:08:50.571 --> 00:08:54.391
And your design system can be
a catalyst for this kind of change, but

150
00:08:54.391 --> 00:08:56.347
it's not going to do it on its own.

151
00:08:56.347 --> 00:08:58.049
